                            ></path>
                        </svg>
                    </a>
                    <a
                        href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/akronymcr?originalSubdomain=co"
                        target="_blank"
                        aria-label="LinkedIn"
                        class="hover:opacity-80"
                    >
                        <svg
                            class="w-5 h-5"
                            fill="currentColor"
                            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        >
                            <path
                                d="M19 0h-14c-2.761 0-5 2.239-5 5v14c0 2.761 2.239 5 5 5h14c2.761 0 5-2.239 5-5v-14c0-2.761-2.239-5-5-5zm-11 19h-3v-10h3v10zm-1.5-11.268c-.966 0-1.75-.784-1.75-1.75s.784-1.75 1.75-1.75 1.75.784 1.75 1.75-.784 1.75-1.75 1.75zm13.5 11.268h-3v-5.604c0-1.337-.026-3.063-1.868-3.063-1.868 0-2.154 1.459-2.154 2.967v5.7h-3v-10h2.881v1.367h.041c.401-.761 1.381-1.563 2.841-1.563 3.039 0 3.6 2.001 3.6 4.601v5.595z"
